{"tid":1275531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠玩法","createTime":"2019-07-01T20:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T20:44:32.000Z","uid":224892,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"af552f18ec689091a92e38dc292a00fef2ce88bb","tid":1275531,"uid":224892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:31:20.000Z","msg":"而家林奠想將所有錯推晒落去義士身上，令人忽略問題嘅根源，即係佢地，令好多原本跟風反對逃犯條例嘅人產生盲點，令人覺得係義士錯<br />\n但係我地清楚明白問題喺邊，所以要更加義無反顧咁支持義士，不割席"},{"pid":"caef34a5ce7f9c67fcd39d9f9592933ba37178e0","tid":1275531,"uid":99018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:34:58.000Z","msg":"重覆多次記者條問題<br />\n和理非同衝擊既訴求一樣<br />\n咁你會唔會回應和理非遊行既訴求<br />\n林奠:"},{"pid":"a348ddbaf8b032a6f8b0cd097ae1b74eebfea0a1","tid":1275531,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:38:04.000Z","msg":"大家要記住責任在林鄭 唔好睇完佢個記者會比佢分化<br />\n<br />\n和平示威；200萬人視若無物<br />\n勇武抗爭； 被社會譴責 <br />\n<br />\n我明和理非既人未必認同勇武手段<br />\n但要記住 兩派系人目標一樣 <br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n只有兩邊合作才能有機<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkjuicynews/videos/650443418428542/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkjuicynews%2Fvideos%2F650443418428542%2F&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C7Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=80ad8afb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkjuicynews/videos/650443418428542/</a><br />\n<br />\n只要唔割 政府就贏既機會係零"},{"pid":"b1c9559f1918673fdda8e85b66ab76c73575feb1","tid":1275531,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:38:20.000Z","msg":"不停重覆佢想TVB 報嘅野，好暴力，有毒粉，明明條問題唔相關都夾硬講兩句"},{"pid":"130ead2c03066f9c9d15d1ec10799744a85e4883","tid":1275531,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1c9559f1918673fdda8e85b66ab76c73575feb1","tid":1275531,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:38:20.000Z","msg":"不停重覆佢想TVB 報嘅野，好暴力，有毒粉，明明條問題唔相關都夾硬講兩句"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:39:07.000Z","msg":"08